{3: 'Lee sits at a table in the lounge. In front of him are three stacks of black cards.'}
{3: "Karenina sits across from him, her face expressionless and her eyes darting between the cards she's holding in her hands. Some time has passed before she squeezes out a few words."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Lu... did she really beat you three times?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Good morning.', 3: '14', 4: 'What are you guys doing?', 5: '16'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Ah! H-how long have you been standing here?!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Isn't it obvious? I thought you'd recognize these common items.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'When did you sneak up on me?', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Karenina and I are playing cards.', 4: '1'}
{2: "Didn't know you guys were into this sort of thing.", 3: '20', 4: 'Is it really okay to gamble in the lounge?', 5: '25'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "W-what's wrong with playing cards?!", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Hey, you got a problem with me?', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'I will beat the crap out of you Gray Ravens. Just you wait!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "It's just a mathematical game that involves a pecuniary arrangement. I don't see what's inappropriate about it.", 4: '1'}
{2: "Can't argue with that...", 3: '28'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Morning, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Morning, Commandant. You're early today.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Finally have some free time.', 3: '36', 4: 'So are you.', 5: '36'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Good morning, Commandant.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'What are you guys up to?', 3: '38'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Bianca was just telling us about this couple in a...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "J-just... Commandant doesn't have time for this...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'What?', 3: '44', 4: 'Hiding something from me?', 5: '44'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Nothing. I was just telling them stories.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Is that so?', 3: '46', 4: "I feel like I'm onto something.", 5: '50'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Oh, and Commandant, I think I just saw Kamui coming by!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "There's absolutely nothing. You're just being paranoid, Commandant!", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Just exchanging some anecdotes.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'I-I think I just saw Kamui looking for Commandant...', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Yeah, I saw him too. With Chrome, the Strike Hawk leader.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Did they come for me?', 3: '58', 4: "I hope it's not a new mission.", 5: '58'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory17.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "It does nothing to help our mission, not to mention I don't have time for it.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'I just want to give it a try!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Your time and energy would be better spent on training. Have you finished the tactical drills I gave you?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Besides, I doubt Commandant would go along with the idea.', 4: '1'}
{2: "How do you know if you don't ask?", 3: '69', 4: 'What idea?', 5: '69'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Ah, Commandant!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Chrome and I were just talking about...', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "Overruled. And don't make me repeat myself.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "At least let Commandant weigh in! You value Commandant's opinion, don't you?", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "Commandant, I apologize for my team member's behavior.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'What is this about exactly?', 3: '75', 4: "It's fine. I'm used to it.", 5: '77'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "I'm really sorry, but it's just some trivial matter.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Nothing you should be concerned about.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "See? Commandant said it's fine!", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "It's nothing to be proud of.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "You're dismissed. I will see you in an hour in the holographic training hall.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Ugh, you are the worst!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "You're just trying to get rid of me so you can have Commandant all to yourself!", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Don't listen to him, Commandant!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Yeah, yeah, yeah.', 3: '84', 4: 'Good luck.', 5: '84'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Sorry for the inconvenience caused, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: "Don't sweat it.", 3: '90', 4: 'You can make it up to me.', 5: '94'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Feel free to contact me if you need my help with anything.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'After all, Strike Hawk and Gray Raven are becoming close partners.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "If you need someone to discuss tactics with, I'm always available.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "You're right. Maybe I can give you something as a thank-you gift.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "Next time I see something that's useful to you, I'll bring it over.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Okay.', 3: '100', 4: 'I was just kidding.', 5: '98'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "Oh, don't take it the wrong way. I was just trying to show you my appreciation for looking out for Strike Hawk.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "If you don't think that's appropriate, then I can only express my appreciation verbally.", 4: '1'}
{2: "It's the thought that counts.", 3: '100', 4: 'No need to go out of your way.', 5: '100'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "Okay then, I'll get back to work.", 4: '1'}
